page.title: 07LORRAINE'S DAY,FT.AUGUSTUS(1
page.content: When I wake up I get out of bed,then I get washed and dressed.I go down stairs and get my brekfast ,usually yogurt and a glass of lemonade.After that I get my bag and coat and go to school.When I get to school I wait for Julia to come.When she comes we talk until the bell goes at half past nine,when we have to go into the classroom. First we discuss world affairs, followed by maths work.At eleven o'clock we get a fifteen minute interval.When we go back into the classroom we usually do maths until ten past twelve when we get our lunch time break.I go home for my lunch and when I come back to school Julia and I usually walk about the school or play football.At twenty past one we have to go back into the classroom.
